599
00:35:46,140 --> 00:35:47,060
Look.

600
00:35:48,340 --> 00:35:48,700
(Deeds of Purchase)

601
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:49,820
From today on,
(Deeds of Purchase)

602
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:50,460
(Deeds of Purchase)

603
00:35:50,460 --> 00:35:51,260
the house
(Deeds of Purchase)

604
00:35:51,260 --> 00:35:52,340
