608
00:35:56,620 --> 00:35:57,340
Leader.

609
00:35:57,540 --> 00:35:58,820
The title deeds.

610
00:35:58,980 --> 00:36:04,780
(Deeds of Purchase to the buyer Shang Xirui)

611
