622
00:36:41,100 --> 00:36:41,940
Good.

623
00:36:42,780 --> 00:36:43,700
Take the title deed.

624
00:36:44,660 --> 00:36:45,380
Mr. Shang.

625
00:36:46,380 --> 00:36:47,260
