780
00:42:46,540 --> 00:42:47,260
Leader.

781
00:42:47,940 --> 00:42:50,300
-Leader.
-Leader.

782
00:42:50,660 --> 00:42:51,220
-Leader.
-Xirui.

783
00:42:51,220 --> 00:42:51,900
When we are there,

784
00:42:51,900 --> 00:42:52,980
