790
00:43:01,340 --> 00:43:02,300
Good idea.

791
00:43:02,300 --> 00:43:02,860
Go ahead.

792
00:43:02,980 --> 00:43:03,860
Right.

793
00:43:03,860 --> 00:43:04,580
Go. Go.

794
00:43:05,140 --> 00:43:05,860
